TO INSTALL Colortemp GUI Indicator, simply execute the install.sh file as root.
To run the GUI indicator, use terminal command "colortemp" or search for "colortemp" in applications menu.

Installer currently works only for Ubuntu versions 14.04 and before, thanks to Pyinstaler majorly screwing up on newer distros.

Kindly send your feedback to 'rajagopalvenkat@outlook.com'.


